fromPlaintext

public static final HtmlClosure fromPlaintext(String text)
Convert a plaintext String into a HtmlClosure that emits the HTML-escaped form of the String. If you are using this in a GXP, you are doing something wrong. GXP is designed to handle all escaping for you.

fromLocalizable

Create a HtmlClosure based on a Localizable. The contents of the Localizable will be escaped on output.
